        "
        mov r0, 0
        mov r1, 5
        mov r2, 4
        mov r3, 6
        jlt r1, r2, +2

        exit
        mov r0, 1
        exit",
        [],
        (),
        0,
        { |_vm, res: Result| { res.unwrap() == 0x1 } },
        9
    );
}
